videos.headline: Ross scores 96-yard kick return TD for Ohio
videos.description: Julian Ross evades the Bowling Green defense en route to a 96-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ross scores 96-yard kick return TD for Ohio) 2020/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio's Tuggle breaks free for 70-yard TD
videos.description: On the first play of the drive, De'Montre Tuggle avoids a tackle and doesn't look back as he speeds for his second touchdown of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio's Tuggle breaks free for 70-yard TD) 2020/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: McDonald zips 26-yard pass to Kinsey for Bowling Green TD
videos.description: Matt McDonald throws a perfect pass to Javonte Kinsey to cut into Ohio's lead.
